1
00:00:31,540 --> 00:00:35,780
=Cases Between Us=

2
00:00:35,980 --> 00:00:38,860
=Episode 32=

3
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:45,600
Are you a cat?

4
00:00:45,856 --> 00:00:47,240
Instead of using the front door,

5
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:49,160
you're climbing in through windows.

6
00:00:50,600 --> 00:00:51,680
You're still up.

7
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:55,640
How is your injury?

8
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:56,640
Injury?

9
00:00:57,920 --> 00:00:59,440
There's no injury.

10
00:00:59,450 --> 00:01:00,600
What? I'm perfectly fine.

11
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,440
Take it off.

12
00:01:02,680 --> 00:01:03,960
Father, who told you that?

13
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:05,080
Take it off!

14
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:11,280
I'm healed.

15
00:01:16,480 --> 00:01:17,640
Your sister hid it from me.

16
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,280
Yuan Hong hid it from me.

17
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:21,480
Even the servants kept it from me.

18
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,800
Do you even see me

19
00:01:22,800 --> 00:01:23,880
as your father anymore?

20
00:01:25,600 --> 00:01:27,280
It was just a flesh wound.

21
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,240
Yuan Hong...

22
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:30,480
Yuan Hong is the Marshal's son.

23
00:01:30,480 --> 00:01:32,280
He'll always have people protecting him.

24
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,000
And you?

25
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,160
You're the only son of the Zhao family.

26
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:36,440
If you keep this up,

27
00:01:36,440 --> 00:01:38,160
our family line ends with you.

28
00:01:38,288 --> 00:01:40,560
But you've always
supported me in solving cases.

29
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,200
Father.

30
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:43,280
You were the one
who got me the consultant position.

31
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,280
Fine. I got it for you,

32
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,480
and I can take it away.

33
00:01:45,632 --> 00:01:46,480
Starting tomorrow,

34
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,640
you're done being a police consultant.

35
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,200
No.

36
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:48,520
Father.

37
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:49,880
Father, please calm down. Calm down.

38
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:50,800
I'll be more careful.

39
00:01:50,800 --> 00:01:51,680
Take this.

40
00:01:52,220 --> 00:01:54,220
(Zhao Shaoshang, RMS Empress of Canada)

41
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,760
What is this?

42
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:56,800
A ticket to America.

43
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,480
Yale.

44
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,680
Everything has been arranged.

45
00:01:59,712 --> 00:02:01,408
You're leaving
after the Chinese New Year.

46
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:02,840
You're sending me away?

47
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:04,240
I... I'm not going.

48
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,520
You don't get a choice.

49
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:09,080
Yuan Hong and I
still have cases to finish.

50
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:09,696
Lock him in.

51
00:02:09,712 --> 00:02:12,080
Without my permission,
he doesn't leave this room.

52
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,320
- Yes, Master.
- Yes, Master.

53
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,240
You're grounding me.

54
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,400
Father,

55
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,400
why send Shaoshang to America
all of a sudden?

56
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:36,840
He's grown these past few months.

57
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,240
You've seen it yourself.

58
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:40,840
Do you know he got hurt?

59
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,560
He promised me
he wouldn't investigate anymore.

60
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:46,160
I'll keep an eye on him too.

61
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:49,640
Besides, he's an adult now.

62
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:51,520
He has a mind of his own.

63
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,920
You can't force him, Father.

64
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:56,040
Do you think getting hurt
was just an accident?

65
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:58,520
Do you know the kind of people
he has crossed?

66
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:08,360
This so-called Republic

67
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:11,560
is just another stage for the warlords.

68
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:15,120
One faction steps down,
another steps up.

69
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:20,960
Power belongs to the men with guns.

70
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:22,840
We civil officials

71
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:24,720
are little more than ornaments.

72
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,080
To buy weapons

73
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,680
from the foreigners,

74
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,760
they'll squeeze the people dry

75
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,080
and stop at nothing.

76
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:37,440
They stoop to anything.

77
00:03:38,120 --> 00:03:40,400
Yuan Hong has the Marshal
to protect him.

78
00:03:40,720 --> 00:03:41,720
But what about Shaoshang?

79
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,000
One day, he could end up dead

80
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:47,280
without ever knowing who killed him.

81
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,960
Father.

82
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,040
Wan'er.

83
00:03:58,120 --> 00:03:59,800
All your mother and I ever wanted

84
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:04,560
was for this family to survive
these troubled times.

85
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:07,320
We never dreamed of fame and glory.

86
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:10,640
Don't let our wealth fool you.

87
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:14,200
When power shifts,

88
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,080
the Zhao family is no more than an ant.

89
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:19,680
I don't ask for anything else.

90
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,840
I just want the two of you

91
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,600
to stay alive

92
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,800
in this terrible world.

93
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,520
Live well.

94
00:05:01,320 --> 00:05:02,280
Mr. Jizhi.

95
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,920
The Tieguanyin tea leaves are ready.

96
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,120
Top quality.

97
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,680
I'm sure you'll be pleased.

98
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,880
Though...

99
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:19,920
I heard

100
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,440
General Chen got hold of

101
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:23,480
a rare batch of Wuyi black tea

102
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,360
to present to the British.

103
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:28,800
I'm rather envious.

104
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,280
Take the west passage.
I'll draw them away.

105
00:05:35,290 --> 00:05:35,840
Yes, sir.

106
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,360
Assassin!

107
00:05:50,160 --> 00:05:51,480
If you want to live, come with me.

108
00:05:55,880 --> 00:05:57,520
You seem awfully familiar

109
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,920
with the Japanese compound.

110
00:05:59,280 --> 00:06:00,320
Protecting you

111
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,600
is my duty.

112
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,760
Does that duty

113
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:07,120
include doing business
with the Japanese?

114
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,120
Young Master,

115
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:10,360
you shouldn't have come tonight.

116
00:06:11,960 --> 00:06:12,720
Since when

117
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,040
do you tell me what to do?

118
00:06:16,528 --> 00:06:17,568
Keep digging like this

119
00:06:17,568 --> 00:06:19,392
is throwing yourself
against a brick wall.

120
00:06:19,536 --> 00:06:20,832
You'll never reach the truth.

121
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,720
Because in this game,

122
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,000
you don't even have a seat at the table.

123
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,120
You know how my mother died.

124
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:34,400
I've served the Marshal for 20 years.

125
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:35,800
I've learned one thing.

126
00:06:36,256 --> 00:06:37,840
The people who accomplish great things

127
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:39,360
rarely have the luxury of choice.

128
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,920
The Marshal isn't just your father

129
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:41,680
or Madam's husband.

130
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:43,200
He's the hope of countless people.

131
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,520
There are some choices

132
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,760
he simply couldn't make.

133
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,120
Couldn't make?

134
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,880
What about my mother?

135
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,800
She didn't deserve to die.

136
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,520
I was an orphan.

137
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:06,120
I was sold to the mines as a child.

138
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,600
I lived worse than a dog.

139
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,760
When I was 12,

140
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:12,240
I killed an overseer

141
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,560
who kept beating me with a shovel.

142
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,160
While I was on the run,

143
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,200
the Marshal saved me.

144
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,560
He gave me a full meal.

145
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:19,800
From that day on,

146
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:20,400
I swore

147
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,040
to devote my life to him.

148
00:07:22,880 --> 00:07:24,280
He told me something.

149
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:27,680
"In this world, you're either the meat

150
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,720
or the knife."

151
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:38,440
Today, I'll leave those words with you.

152
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:41,280
If you want the truth,

153
00:07:41,536 --> 00:07:43,456
you'd better have a knife
in your hand first.

154
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,640
(Chief Yuan,)

155
00:08:30,896 --> 00:08:32,680
(here's the rent for the past few days.)

156
00:08:32,840 --> 00:08:33,640
(Keep the change.)

157
00:08:34,032 --> 00:08:35,480
(When Du Wenjiu finishes
testing the drink can,)

158
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,280
(let me know.)

159
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:38,688
(Come to my place
for Chinese New Year's Eve dinner.)

160
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,960
(Your best partner,)

161
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,240
(Zhao Shaoshang.)

162
00:08:47,620 --> 00:08:51,620
(Peking Union Medical College
Test Report)

163
00:08:52,180 --> 00:08:56,120
♪Good or evil, who dares to speak out?♪

164
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:04,780
♪Or perhaps we'd rather stay silent♪

165
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:10,930
♪Who can ever foresee this?♪

166
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:19,360
♪Before we can move forward once again♪

167
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:25,760
♪We'll walk through this dark night
together♪

168
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:29,960
♪This road is full of dangers♪

169
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:36,450
♪How can we
keep walking side by side?♪

170
00:09:36,450 --> 00:09:43,470
♪The wave of fate slowly pulls us apart♪

171
00:09:43,650 --> 00:09:50,440
♪Though we share the same sea,
we drift in different areas♪

172
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:54,700
♪The tide has no choice♪

173
00:09:55,140 --> 00:10:04,120
♪The more we try to draw near,
the farther we're swept apart♪

174
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:11,600
♪Every memory remains etched
before my eyes♪

175
00:10:11,900 --> 00:10:20,580
♪Why does my gaze return to
that silent look again and again?♪

176
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:25,160
♪Against the unseen course of fate♪

177
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:27,040
(Commissioner's Office)
You're resigning?

178
00:10:27,808 --> 00:10:29,728
My father is tied up
with military affairs.

179
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,160
I'm going back to help him.

180
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:34,360
To help your father?

181
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,960
Cut the excuses.

182
00:10:36,960 --> 00:10:38,840
What happens to Division Four
after you leave?

183
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:41,080
Yang Dezhi has been with the department
for eight years.

184
00:10:41,296 --> 00:10:42,380
It's time he got promoted.

185
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:44,840
Fair enough.

186
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:48,120
But the paperwork's a bit of a hassle.

187
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,184
If you don't approve it,

188
00:10:49,216 --> 00:10:50,640
I'll have a chat with some friends

189
00:10:50,672 --> 00:10:51,920
at the Administrative Court

190
00:10:51,984 --> 00:10:53,000
about where last month's

191
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,880
confiscated customs goods ended up.

192
00:10:56,280 --> 00:10:57,920
Approved.

193
00:10:58,320 --> 00:11:00,600
Yang Dezhi takes over tomorrow.

194
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,920
Go be a good son.

195
00:11:05,376 --> 00:11:06,600
Thank you, Commissioner.

196
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,440
Don't mention it.

197
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:12,840
Chief,

198
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,280
are you really leaving?

199
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:15,440
This is so sudden.

200
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:17,880
Division Four

201
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:18,720
is all yours now.

202
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:19,840
Do a good job.

203
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,160
Me?

204
00:11:21,160 --> 00:11:21,600
Wait.

205
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,800
What about Young Master Zhao?

206
00:11:22,800 --> 00:11:24,840
Aren't you going to tell him?

207
00:11:27,760 --> 00:11:29,040
There's no need.

208
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,200
Did something happen?

209
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:42,420
(Jingshi Police Department)

210
00:11:43,160 --> 00:11:43,880
Chief Yuan.

211
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:48,080
May I have a word?

212
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,120
I'll cut to the chase.

213
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:59,160
I'm here because of Shaoshang.

214
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,280
I've had him resign

215
00:12:02,368 --> 00:12:03,680
as an investigative consultant.

216
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:04,840
From now on,

217
00:12:05,160 --> 00:12:07,280
he won't be involved in your cases.

218
00:12:09,008 --> 00:12:10,040
You've worried too much.

219
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,760
I've resigned as well.

220
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:14,400
If you're keeping him away
because of me,

221
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:17,080
there's no need for him to leave.

222
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:19,120
He'd make a fine policeman.

223
00:12:19,360 --> 00:12:20,600
You should respect his choice.

224
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,040
If I keep respecting his choice,

225
00:12:24,040 --> 00:12:25,760
he'll end up dead.

226
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,080
Last time was an accident.

227
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:29,280
As long as I...

228
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,200
Yuan Hong,

229
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:34,112
do you know what it means
to stir up the hornet's nest?

230
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,040
You've torn up all the grass

231
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,240
around the nest.

232
00:12:37,552 --> 00:12:39,000
Even a cornered rabbit will bite.

233
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,760
Never mind a nest of vipers.

234
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:47,400
The purge has begun.

235
00:12:48,240 --> 00:12:49,760
I'm struggling to protect myself,

236
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,200
let alone Shaoshang.

237
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:56,160
So I've decided to send him abroad.

238
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,320
Abroad?

239
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:01,760
To study.

240
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,280
But I know my son.

241
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,920
He's as stubborn as a mule.

242
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:07,800
That's why I came to you today.

243
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,120
I hope you'll help

244
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,680
talk some sense into him.

245
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,400
Please.

246
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,360
What?

247
00:13:46,656 --> 00:13:47,664
Do you all need a show

248
00:13:47,712 --> 00:13:48,800
while Young Master eats?

249
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:49,760
Get out.

250
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:57,600
Young Master.

251
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:58,800
How was it?

252
00:13:59,160 --> 00:14:00,120
What did Yuan Hong say?

253
00:14:02,520 --> 00:14:03,160
Answer me.

254
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,080
Cat got your tongue?

255
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:06,320
Chief Yuan resigned.

256
00:14:09,760 --> 00:14:10,600
What did you say?

257
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:15,280
Chief Yuan resigned.

258
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,120
He reported for duty
with the army today.

259
00:14:17,328 --> 00:14:19,280
The Marshal appointed him
division commander.

260
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:28,640
- One, two.
- One, two.

261
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:29,800
Put some spirit into it!

262
00:14:37,040 --> 00:14:38,720
I gathered you all here today

263
00:14:40,480 --> 00:14:41,960
for one reason.

264
00:14:42,920 --> 00:14:44,280
Effective immediately,

265
00:14:45,400 --> 00:14:47,240
Yuan Hong rejoins the army

266
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,880
as commander of the Third Division.

267
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:56,400
The Third Division
is the backbone of our forces.

268
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,960
The spearhead
that breaks the enemy's line.

269
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:02,160
With foreign threats

270
00:15:02,160 --> 00:15:03,320
closing in on every side,

271
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,040
we need capable leaders.

272
00:15:06,688 --> 00:15:08,656
I promote talent,
not because he's my son.

273
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,720
I've put him in this position today

274
00:15:12,160 --> 00:15:15,040
because I hope all of you will

275
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:16,360
watch over him,

276
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:17,800
support him,

277
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,920
and guide him.

278
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,480
May my son and I

279
00:15:22,280 --> 00:15:23,840
stand shoulder to shoulder with you all,

280
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,200
build a stronger army,

281
00:15:25,376 --> 00:15:26,752
wipe away our nation's shame,

282
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,040
and restore this land.

283
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:38,340
(Appointment Letter: Yuan Hong is hereby
appointed Commander of Third Division)

284
00:15:49,072 --> 00:15:50,400
Congratulations, Young Marshal.

285
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:53,360
The Third Division
will serve you with unwavering loyalty.

286
00:15:54,512 --> 00:15:57,408
- We'll serve you with loyalty!
- We'll serve you with loyalty!

287
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:07,600
Young Master, maybe
you should think this through.

288
00:16:07,616 --> 00:16:08,720
What if Master finds out

289
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:10,000
that you sneak out?

290
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:11,120
There's no time.

291
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:12,680
Yuan Hong must be in trouble.

292
00:16:12,920 --> 00:16:13,920
I need to find him.

293
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:24,600
Young Master.

294
00:16:24,600 --> 00:16:25,480
Be careful.

295
00:16:30,144 --> 00:16:31,690
(Type 83 pistol ammunition, 600 rounds)

296
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:39,680
Stop!

297
00:16:40,040 --> 00:16:40,720
Who goes there?

298
00:16:43,280 --> 00:16:44,320
I'm with the police.

299
00:16:44,330 --> 00:16:45,360
I'm here to see Yuan Hong.

300
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,720
Identification.

301
00:16:50,280 --> 00:16:50,840
Seize him.

302
00:16:52,840 --> 00:16:53,920
I'm Yuan Hong's friend.

303
00:16:54,272 --> 00:16:56,200
(Pingbei Mobile First Battalion)
Let go! Let go!

304
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,880
How dare you trespass

305
00:16:57,880 --> 00:16:58,920
on a military base!

306
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,080
Yuan Hong!

307
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,160
Yuan Hong!

308
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,520
Yuan Hong!

309
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:39,560
Report, Commander.

310
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:41,328
We apprehended a suspicious individual.

311
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,280
Let him go.

312
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:43,080
But...

313
00:17:43,440 --> 00:17:44,400
Let him go!

314
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:46,080
Let him go!

315
00:18:23,660 --> 00:18:26,540
(End of Episode 32)

316
00:18:27,721 --> 00:18:29,361
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

317
00:18:29,361 --> 00:18:30,901
♪Troubled times
are but a laughing matter♪

318
00:18:30,901 --> 00:18:32,151
♪However, the world changes♪

319
00:18:32,151 --> 00:18:34,071
♪You'll still be by my side♪

320
00:18:34,071 --> 00:18:35,761
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

321
00:18:35,761 --> 00:18:37,331
♪Praise and blame come and go♪

322
00:18:37,331 --> 00:18:38,901
♪If this is my final chapter♪

323
00:18:38,901 --> 00:18:41,401
♪I'll solve this mystery with you♪
